<br>
Say, if we had 3 to 4 groups of 44 to 52 lvl Toons, with 1 to 2 groups of 53 to 60 lvl Escorts, these raids would be simple.  The big boys and girls go in clear the path, keep the crew ready for war, this speeds up down time, because you wont have to waste mana on the &quot; Protectors&quot; of Naggy and Vox, i.e. Ice Giants, Fire Giants, etc.  <br>
<br>
So, you get your crew, zoned in, Buffed up to their ears and just have the Monster Group, which I know we could form some Monster Crews in this Federation, have this Monster Group or Groups, mow down the guards etc.  Then the crew, goes in, killing the dragon and we get Epic pieces for Federation Members.  And I want to make sure all understand, any epic piece that drops, goes to someone that needs it for their epics!  But the remains loot can be rolled on a need before greed style.  Its just sad to see people pawning Red Dragon Scales, White Dragon Scales and other epics, to make some quick cash, its not like these things can be foraged, lol.<br>
<br>
Just an idea, I would love some feedback on this, Thanks all.<br>
<br>
Wyldebear Tundrahunter<br>
